data.name: Develop bias testing protocol for chatbot responses
data.notes:
Establish testing framework to identify and mitigate bias in AI responses:
    Test chatbot across diverse user scenarios and demographics
    Identify potential discriminatory language or unequal service outcomes
    Review training data for bias and representation gaps
    Document bias mitigation strategies and corrective actions
    Set up ongoing monitoring for bias detection post-launch

Aligns with federal responsible AI guidelines and ethical AI deployment standards.

data.name: Submit ATO package to authorizing official
data.notes:
Prepare and submit Authority to Operate (ATO) documentation package including:
    System Security Plan (SSP)
    Risk assessment and mitigation strategies
    Security control implementation evidence
    Privacy Impact Assessment (PIA)
    Continuous monitoring plan
    Incident response procedures

Work with ISSO (Information System Security Officer) and authorizing official to ensure all FedRAMP requirements are met for production deployment.
